        <div n="X03-1071">
          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-X03-1071-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-X03-1071-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-X03-1071-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">Written by the D<hi rend="small-caps">EAN</hi> in the Name of D<hi rend="small-caps">AN </hi>J<hi rend="small-caps">ACKSON</hi>.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-X03-1071-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-X03-1071-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-X03-1071-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-X03-1071-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-X03-1071-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-X03-1071-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">W</hi>Earied with saying Grace and Pray'r, 3}</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-2" n="2">I hasten'd down to Country-Air,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-3" n="3">To read your Answer, and prepare</l>
            <l rend="flush-right" xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-4" n="4">Reply to't.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-5" n="5"><lb/>But your fair Lines so grossly flatter, 3}</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-6" n="6">Pray do they praise me or bespatter?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-7" n="7">I much suspect you mean the latter,</l>
            <l rend="flush-right" xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-8" n="8">ah Sly-boot!</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-9" n="9"><lb/>It must be so; what else, alas, 3}</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-10" n="10">Can mean my culling of a Face,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-11" n="11">And all that Stuff of Toilet, Glass,</l>
            <l rend="flush-right" xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-12" n="12">and Box-Comb?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-13" n="13"><lb/>But be't as 'twill, this you must grant, 3}</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-14" n="14">That you're a Dawb, whilst I but paint;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-15" n="15">Then which of us two is the quaint-</l>
            <l rend="flush-right" xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-16" n="16">er Coxcomb?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-17" n="17"><lb/>I value not your Jokes of Noose, 3}</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-18" n="18">Your Gibes and all your foul Abuse,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-19" n="19">More than the Dirt beneath my Shoes,</l>
            <l rend="flush-right" xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-20" n="20">nor fear it.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-21" n="21"><lb/>Yet one Thing vexes me, I own, 3}</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-22" n="22">Thou sorry Scarecrow of Skin and Bone,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-23" n="23">To be call'd lean by a Skeleton,</l>
            <l rend="flush-right" xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-24" n="24">who'd bear it?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-25" n="25"><lb/>'Tis true indeed, to curry Friends, 3}</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-26" n="26">You seem to praise to make amends,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-27" n="27">And yet before your Stanza ends,</l>
            <l rend="flush-right" xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-28" n="28">you flout me.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-29" n="29"><lb/>'Bout latent Charms beneath my Cloaths; 3}</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-30" n="30">For every one that knows me, knows</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-31" n="31">That I have Nothing like my Nose</l>
            <l rend="flush-right" xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-32" n="32">about me.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-33" n="33"><lb/>I pass now where you fleer and laugh, 3}</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-34" n="34">'Cause I call <hi rend="italics">Dan</hi> my better Half!</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-35" n="35">Oh, there you think you have me safe!</l>
            <l rend="flush-right" xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-36" n="36">but hold, Sir.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-37" n="37"><lb/>Is not a Penny often found 3}</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-38" n="38">To be much greater than a Pound?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-39" n="39">By your good Leave, my most profound</l>
            <l rend="flush-right" xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-40" n="40">and bold Sir,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-41" n="41"><lb/><hi rend="italics">Dan</hi>'s noble Mettal, <hi rend="italics">Sherry</hi> base; 3}</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-42" n="42">So <hi rend="italics">Dan</hi>'s the better, though the less,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-43" n="43">An Ounce of Gold's worth ten of Brass,</l>
            <l rend="flush-right" xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-44" n="44">dull Pedant.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-45" n="45"><lb/>As to your Spelling, let me see, 3}</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-46" n="46">If <hi rend="italics">SHE</hi> makes <hi rend="italics">sher</hi>, and <hi rend="italics">RI</hi> makes <hi rend="italics">ry</hi>,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-47" n="47">Good Spelling-Master, your Crany</l>
            <l rend="flush-right" xml:id="swift-X03-1071-line-48" n="48">has lead in't.</l>
          </lg>
